Package UserCode.UserInterfaces

Interface Summary
IConsumer IConsumer Interface - Provides functionality to allow implementations to 'consume' other tokens of type IDisplayObject:
IDisplayable IDisplayable: allows this object to be displayed in a virtual environment of type IWorld.
IInputListener IInputListener: all listeners for input must implement this interface.
IInputPublisher IInputPublisher: publishes input events to all listeners.
ILocation ILocation interface provides methods that allows the manipulation of an objects location.
IUpdatableFactory IUpdatableFactory interface - all implementations can create instances of IUpdatable Tokens to be placed in the aquarium From Chris Blythe's live coding session for week 16.
